rows.label: tlk4750016501_msg0001
rows.name:
Oho! Good to see you back! We haven't
seen you in a while, have we?

rows.label: tlk4750016501_msg0002
rows.name:
The children that land up with Correl
all blossom into fine young specimens.

rows.label: tlk4750016501_msg0003
rows.name:
You've grown into a splendid young
man yourself, Rex. I can attest to that.

rows.label: tlk4750016501_msg0101
rows.name:
We don't often see Driver folks in
these parts! When was the last time,
I wonder.

rows.label: tlk4750016501_msg0102
rows.name:
We get a good few merchants stopping
by though. Because of the port, see.

rows.label: tlk4750016501_msg0103
rows.name:
Aye, it's nothing fancy, but it's our
home, and you're very welcome!
